room_title: Escape room "The Missing Starlet" by Elusive Escape Rooms in Wisconsin Dells
room_address: 1425 Wisconsin Dells Parkway Suite 3 Wisconsin Dells, WI 53965
room_description: We’re coming to the end of the 1950s – A time when every young woman has aspirations of becoming the next Marilyn Monroe. Our starlet is no different. She is beautiful, talented, and on her way to the top, when out of nowhere she’s kidnapped. The private investigator needs your help on the case. Who did it? Why? Can you crack the case and escape the room before this becomes another Hollywood mystery?
